archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This is a first braindump of how things are currently looking for Tietoevry connect. The goals are not the formal goals from leadership, just a representation of what we are trying to achieve, which i put down on paper as a discussion point, with the intention of revising this over time.
I took this down to the next level of detail to try to understand some of the challenges we are facing, and to get in some requirements and goals to meet some of the challenges. The challenges are mostly assessments.
So far I have walked through this with Sami & Lingskog.
